Invocation Name: institute news
des:
Access a variety IEEE news sources through RSS feeds. You can ask Alexa to read you the most up to date articles from each source, to stay informed of the most breaking edge engineering projects and ideas.

You can also customize your own news stream by adding several feeds to your favorites. For instance, simply say add 'Transmitter' to favorites.
